<plot>Marsha, a World War II era housewife, has already lost her first son in a war she no longer believes in. Her husband Sam, a firm patriot, decides it is time their youngest son George enlist to fight as his brother had. Faced with the threat of losing another son, Marsha decides she must stand against Sam, and stop him from sending their last child off to die for his country.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569310</url></doc>
